{"tid":245223,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"取代朗尼做10號！5‧21曼聯官宣簽J神","createTime":"2017-05-16T05:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T13:09:45.000Z","uid":8968,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35830bb3b07bd37301088953bc81ff42dc26f0a6","tid":245223,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/132531_240618b60d198773a90def42ddeb3496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F132531_240618b60d198773a90def42ddeb3496.jpg&h=4d202088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞電台《Caracol》爆料，曼聯同皇家馬德里已經決定喺5月21號，官方宣布占士洛迪古斯嘅轉會消息，仲話佢登陸奧脫福球場後，將會取代朗尼成為紅魔10號波衫新主人，即係月巴要執包袱走人。據知J神嘅轉會費唔低於8,000萬歐元，而且佢已經同曼聯傾妥個人條件，所以皇馬日前喺西甲主場以4:1擊敗西維爾，佢被換出後360度拍手向球迷致謝，預先同巴拿貝球迷講再見呀！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170516/mobile/bkn-20170516103017804-0516_00882_001.html#popupGallery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170516%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170516103017804-0516_00882_001.html%23popupGallery&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1bccabe2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170516/mobile/bkn-20170516103017804-0516_00882_001.html#popupGallery</a>"},{"pid":"02c287ec685142d08b35186e10385a093b75f7ef","tid":245223,"uid":76437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6662fbdb2d12aba647687a459dd1f78be6c11b9","tid":245223,"uid":12154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"J朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550497117bf94a76d7784b72a4de3d201f902da4","tid":245223,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好呀</span></spa